-- Russian Gay Activists Attacked in St. Petersburg, Interfax Says
-- B y   S t e p a n   K r a v c h e n k o
-- 2012-05-17T18:20:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-17/russian-gay-activists-attacked-in-st-petersburg-interfax-says.html
Russian gay activists were attacked
today in St. Petersburg, Interfax newswire said, citing a report
by its correspondent on the scene.  Scores of masked men stopped a bus carrying the activists
from an anti-homophobia rally and started beating them, Interfax
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stepan Kravchenko in Moscow at 
 skravchenko@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
